MESSAGE.value: Replaced Mysql driver with Hikari, allowing connection pooling.
Added /balance and implemented a part of the custom currency. Also added database saving when the player quits, would make it asynchronous later.
Implemented a runnable to give XP every 10 minutes, and implemented XP system with levels.
Added Redis database which is going to be used as caching system.
Added custom permissions check, and Wildcard handling by injecting into the entity.
Decided to switch only to Redis as persistent storage, because MySQL isnt worth it for such plugin. Redis would be enough.
